  <p>
    Effusion Labs is a digital studio and knowledge base focused on creative synthesis, technical
    experimentation, and traceable longform thinking.
  </p>

  <p>
    The site is organized into four primary content areas: <strong>Sparks</strong>,
    <strong>Concepts</strong>, <strong>Projects</strong>, and <strong>Meta</strong>. Together they
    document how fragments evolve into models, prototypes, and operating methods.
  </p>

  <p>
    This is not a brochure site. It is a living static archive built to make structure visible:
    source material, intermediate reasoning, design systems, and experiments are meant to remain
    inspectable.
  </p>

